NUMBER 1365
NAME Chlry'est, Healer
INDOOR_FLOOR
HEALER
DAY_LIGHT
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
This small area has been devoted to the arts of healing. Small
shelves are seated into the trunk of the tree, and lined with
numerous bottles of various shapes and sizes, written upon
in aelven script. A heavy, medicinal scent lingers on the air,
yet it itself is full of the heady magic of the living trees. A 
small opening leads back to a nearby tree. A large hand-painted
sign hangs on the back wall.
*DESCRIPTION_END
