    CONTPLREVENT
    ECHO PLAYER C'ven'ti smiles, and says, "This is our healers place. You can find many such places around Andor. Although we do not prefer war, we have often times been forced into battles that we did not wish. Our age old war with the Dark Ones, or Mardhrel, has given us more pain that we care to admit."
    PLREVENT 3
    CONTPLREVENT 
