NUMBER 1463 
NAME Chlry'est, Landing
FOREST
DAY_LIGHT
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
This large landing winds its way around a massive oak tree.
Numerous bridges connect here, each tied securely with ropes and
bound in with heavy wooden nails. The graceful branches of the
tree shield this area from the worst of the weather. Looking
about, you can see several homes in the trees, and more landings
and bridges scattered about.
*DESCRIPTION_END
ITEM 0 61 VAL2=1396
ITEM 1 61 VAL2=1464
ITEM 2 61 VAL2=1465
ITEM 3 61 
ITEM 4 61 ADJ1=183 VAL2=1467
EXTEND 0 leading to the Gathering
EXTEND 1 leading to C'ven'ti's home
EXTEND 2 leading to another landing
EXTEND 3 leading to a private home
EXTEND 4 leading to the Temple
IFPREVERB GO 3
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER You walk across the bridge, and come to a locked door. Obviously they do not wish guests. You return.
  ECHO OTHERS %N walks across the bridge and promptly returns.
ENDIF  
