NUMBER 1464
NAME Chlry'est, C'ven'ti's home
INDOOR_FLOOR
FIXED_LIGHT
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
This beautiful tree overlooks the small streambed. Numerous personal
items are scattered about, and above the mantle, a single bo-stick
is displayed. A simple sofa rests comfortably in front of the fireplace,
and a small cradle sits near the window. A small, double bed rests on
the far side of the room as well. A bridge leads back to the nearby landing.
*DESCRIPTION_END
ITEM 0 61 VAL2=1463
ITEM 1 84
ITEM 2 1911
ITEM 3 5 ADJ1=678
IFTOUCH 3
  CLEARVERB 
  ECHO PLAYER The bo-stick is hung well out of reach.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB TAKE 3
  CLEARVERB 
  ECHO PLAYER The bo-stick is hung firmly to the wall.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB STEAL 3
  CLEARVERB 
  ECHO PLAYER The bo-stick is hung firmly to the wall.
ENDIF
