CALL 33
FIXED_LIGHT
*DESCRIPTION_START
This smaller landing rests comfortably in the shade of a large oak.
You find yourself deeper into the forest, and much of the rest of the
village is out of sight. Still, more bridges exists, winding their way
through the upper reaches of the trees and dipping down to individual homes.
The scent of a small forge hangs in the air.
*DESCRIPTION_END
