NUMBER 1467
NAME Chlry'est, Temple of Totems
INDOOR_FLOOR
DAY_LIGHT
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
A sense of solemness prevails here, as the altars of the totems are seen.
Each one is nestled into its own niche, while the other five are seen across
a small wooden bridge. Along the inside of the tree, many elegant carvings
of the spirits of each totem can be seen. A small ladder leads down out of 
the tree.
*DESCRIPTION_END
